  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These air raids-- these devastating air raids continued.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's when we left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We left-- we left-- after we lost our, our home, we went to Silesia and tried to-- and because we had friends there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we tried to find a new-- and moved there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We couldn't get any apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything was-- so many were bombed out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had friends there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they put us in, in temporary housing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's when I had to, of course, to, to report immediately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because now it was-- that was the end of 1943-- report to the police department again, fill out those forms again, identify myself as what I am.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I had to-- and also that I'm-- that I'm also available for any work because that's-- that, that goes without saying that you had to-- that was the, the mandatory.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, too, had to and my brother, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was the main object.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and, that, that was an-- that's another chapter which I will I, I--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--can later more discuss in detail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All registered--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they-- but then they would find me work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would get a notification that I have to, you know, report for work for--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--possibly defense-- possibly-- most likely defense work.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
